		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I think getting SMW reproduced on cart with a normal mapper like say MMC3 instead of that crazy Mapper 90  is\would be like a holy grail in the pirate port game scene for the NES.
<br />
<br /> I've always wondered why SMW and\or Bio Miricle AKA Baby Mario have never been hacked to a more common mapper. They both seem to be games popular enough that someone would have took on the job.

		

		</td>
