	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I have hacked the cartridge version of Bio Miracle to MMC5. I also have looked into hacking some mapper 90 games like SMW and Final Fight 3. However, they are programmed so wonky, Final Fight 3 for instance is designed apparently with traps to discourage modification of the game causing crashes when you modify certain parts. I lost interest in trying to hack mapper 90 games when I ran up against that resistance as I have little interest putting alot of effort into hacking a really shitty game. Sorry, but SMW sucks, FF3 sucks, it's just a novelty and one I certainly can do without.

		

		</td>
